<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #FF9800; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 30px; background: #f9f9f9; }
    .reminder-box { background: white; padding: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #FF9800; margin: 20px 0; }
    .urgent-badge { background: #FF5722; color: white; padding: 5px 15px; border-radius: 20px; display: inline-block; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 0.9em; }
    .meeting-link { background: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 15px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
    .meeting-link a { color: white; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 0.9em; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>⏰ Your Session Starts Soon!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <span class="urgent-badge">⚠️ 30 Minutes Remaining</span>
      
      <p>Hey {{custName}},</p>
      
      <div class="reminder-box">
        <p>It's a reminder that your appointment for <strong>Order #{{order_number}}</strong> - <strong>{{packageName}}</strong> is scheduled for:</p>
        <p style="font-size: 1.2em; font-weight: bold; color: #FF9800; text-align: center; margin: 15px 0;">{{dateTime}}</p>
      </div>

      {{#if meetingLink}}
      <div class="meeting-link">
        <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><strong>Please join:</strong></p>
        <p style="margin: 0;"><a href="{{meetingLink}}">{{meetingLink}}</a></p>
      </div>
      {{else}}
      <p style="background: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;">
        <strong>Note:</strong> Meeting link will be available shortly. Please check your email for updates.
      </p>
      {{/if}}

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Best Regards,<br><strong>Better LSAT MCAT Team</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated reminder sent 30 minutes before your scheduled session.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

